the increasing awareness of human rights
in the United Kingdom

00:01:55.360 --> 00:02:00.710
and the growth of a rights culture may have
been partly responsible for these large

00:02:00.710 --> 00:02:01.439
numbers

00:02:01.439 --> 00:02:04.700
the fact that the United Kingdom did not
have a bill

00:02:04.700 --> 00:02:08.700
or charger a bright embedded in its
constitution may

