taken to europe

00:02:11.700 --> 00:02:15.140
because at the absence relevant
legislation

00:02:15.140 --> 00:02:18.650
to redress wrongs in this country

00:02:18.650 --> 00:02:21.770
a movement grew through the nineteen
eighties in nineteen nineties

00:02:21.770 --> 00:02:25.540
